{"tid":2419573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"預算案「減糖」 不再派錢亦沒有公屋免租","createTime":"2021-02-23T11:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T13:04:26.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0ddf78f00251767ab22ccbcb1e06aa3a1b87583d","tid":2419573,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波周三發表新一份財政預算案。消息透露，預算案會提出為失業人士提供百分百擔保的貸款計劃，上限八萬元，而因應財赤高企，這份預算案會「減糖」，不再派錢，亦不會有公屋免租。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波早前已披露新一份財政預算案，封面是青綠色，代表對未來懷抱希望。<br />\n<br />\n受新冠疫情打擊，最新的失業率升至7%，是近17年來的新高。消息透露，新一份預算案會提出，為失業人士提供由政府百分百的擔保貸款計劃。"},{"pid":"93ae40a3533f74735d9dfa665c1f1714431a5ce2","tid":2419573,"uid":90946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"我地冚家咁G持政府竟然咁對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae8593d42b5e6e3fa7662682890368b88f462ef","tid":2419573,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"公屋仔末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0d28c125d3a7f245c898348e139caddce4b454","tid":2419573,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"咁樣對你地既支持者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57f8091eb33db291712c584558e79035f595ad0","tid":2419573,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"有左國安法點解仲會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3636c176a634f7186c0dd0416c43bd4ab8abb169","tid":2419573,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"冇晒攬炒派<br />\n結果仲少咗糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6b451ffb8e3170b78ac023affc2d90bc520dd1","tid":2419573,"uid":3543